{"prompt": "Generate a website for a video game studio. The website should be playful and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>PixelPlay Studios</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #e0f7fa; /* Light blue background */\n            color: #004d40; /* Dark teal for text */\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0077cc 0%, #4dd0e1 100%); /* Vibrant blue gradient */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 100px 20px;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 4em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            max-width: 800px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .content {\n            padding: 60px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .content h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: #0077cc; /* Brand blue for headings */\n        }\n        .games-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            max-width: 1000px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n        .game-card {\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 119, 204, 0.1); /* Subtle blue shadow */\n            overflow: hidden;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid #4dd0e1; /* Light blue border */\n        }\n        .game-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n        }\n        .game-card img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n        }\n        .game-card-content {\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n        .game-card-content h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: #0077cc; /* Brand blue for game titles */\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n        }\n        .game-card-content p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n            line-height: 1.5;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #0077cc; /* Brand blue footer */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n            margin-top: 60px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        .floating-shapes {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            pointer-events: none;\n        }\n        .shape {\n            position: absolute;\n            background-color: rgba(77, 208, 225, 0.3); /* Semi-transparent light blue */\n            border-radius: 50%;\n        }\n        .shape.one { top: 10%; left: 5%; width: 80px; height: 80px; animation: float 5s infinite ease-in-out; }\n        .shape.two { top: 60%; left: 80%; width: 120px; height: 120px; animation: float 7s infinite ease-in-out -2s; }\n        .shape.three { top: 30%; left: 45%; width: 50px; height: 50px; animation: float 6s infinite ease-in-out -4s; }\n        .shape.four { top: 80%; left: 20%; width: 100px; height: 100px; animation: float 5.5s infinite ease-in-out -1s; }\n\n        @keyframes float {\n            0% { transform: translateY(0); }\n            50% { transform: translateY(-30px); }\n            100% { transform: translateY(0); }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"floating-shapes\">\n            <div class=\"shape one\"></div>\n            <div class=\"shape two\"></div>\n            <div class=\"shape three\"></div>\n            <div class=\"shape four\"></div>\n        </div>\n        <h1>PixelPlay Studios</h1>\n        <p>Crafting Worlds, One Pixel at a Time. Dive into our universe of fun and adventure!</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"content\">\n        <h2>Our Latest Creations</h2>\n        <div class=\"games-grid\">\n            <div class=\"game-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/0077cc/ffffff?text=Cosmic+Voyage\" alt=\"Cosmic Voyage Game\">\n                <div class=\"game-card-content\">\n                    <h3>Cosmic Voyage</h3>\n                    <p>Embark on an interstellar journey to explore uncharted galaxies and encounter alien wonders.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"game-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/4dd0e1/ffffff?text=Enchanted+Forest\" alt=\"Enchanted Forest Game\">\n                <div class=\"game-card-content\">\n                    <h3>Enchanted Forest</h3>\n                    <p>Discover magical creatures and solve ancient puzzles in a mystical, ever-changing woodland.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"game-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/0077cc/ffffff?text=Robo+Rumble\" alt=\"Robo Rumble Game\">\n                <div class=\"game-card-content\">\n                    <h3>Robo Rumble</h3>\n                    <p>Build your ultimate robot and battle it out in thrilling arenas against players worldwide.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 PixelPlay Studios. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}